            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic quiescit in pace Lycontius <lb n="2"/>presb&amp;lt;y=I&amp;gt;ter titulum posueru<supplied reason="lost">nt</supplied> <lb n="3"/>fratr<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>s sui Quiriacus et Leosa <lb n="4"/>pridie K<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>l</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> Nov<expan><ex>em</ex><abbr>br</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> pausavit <lb n="5"/>feria q<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>arta</abbr></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der Verstorbene starb am 31. Oktober an einem Donnerstag (feria quarta). Unterhalb der Inschrift Darstellung eines Christograms mit Alpha und Omega.</p>
            </div>
